title: Toro y Moi performs "Tuesday" and more Live on KEXP from 25th Street Recording in Oakland

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Toro y Moi performing live at 25th Street Recording in Oakland, California, during Noise Pop 2025. Recorded February 25, 2025.

Tuesday 00:55
